members.description: The Royale Compiler will inject html into the index.html file.  Surround with "inject_html" tag as follows:  <inject_html> <link rel="stylesheet" href="//code.jquery.com/ui/1.10.2/themes/smoothness/jquery-ui.css" /> <script src="//code.jquery.com/jquery-1.9.1.js"></script> <script src="//code.jquery.com/ui/1.10.2/jquery-ui.js"></script> </inject_html>
